    • Method Detail

      • actuallyPutNextEntry

        void actuallyPutNextEntry(ZipEntry entry)
                   throws IOException
        Called by CustomZipOutputStream.putNextEntry(ZipEntry) and used by impls to put the next entry into the zip file. It is guaranteed that the entry won't be null and the stream will be open. It is also guaranteed that there's no current entry open.
        Parameters:
        entry - The ZipEntry to write.
        Throws:
        IOException

      • actuallyCloseEntry

        void actuallyCloseEntry()

        Called by CustomZipOutputStream.close() and used by impls to close the delegate stream. This method will be called at most once in the lifecycle of the CustomZipOutputStream.

        IOException
